name: CITIBLOX 3 (Summer Night)
description:
[sound on]

YOU are the owner of CITIBLOX 2

This is a set of KEYS.

Keys to a a city called METATROPOLIS

Each is unique, but they can be paired.

In certain combinations they can unlock powers.

Even at night the clouds are underlit with orange,
the color of the night lamp posts gazing up.

Savor this moment - drink in this sky.
The skies of Metatropolis belong to you.

Grab them cheap and follow me at
@HPLOVEBUX

Then the whole picture may become clear . . .
